This package was debianized by Adam Powell <hazelsct@mit.edu> on April 16 2001
based on the petsc source package of 2.0.28 begun August 14 2000

It was downloaded from http://www.mcs.anl.gov/petsc/ as 3.0.0 tarball,
.orig.tar.gz contains the 3.0.0-p0 release.

Upstream authors: Satish Balay, William D. Gropp, Lois Curfman McInnes,
 Barry F. Smith

